title: Hour 2 - NBA Season Preview, Louis Riddick
itunes:title: Hour 2 - NBA Season Preview, Louis Riddick
description:
Dan and the Danettes preview the NBA season which begins tonight. And Dan talks to former NFL Safety and current analyst Louis Riddick stops by with some advice for Denver Broncos QB Russell Wilson.
